{
  "stem": "14156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you know, the people-- we were in civilian clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The only thing, you had the star.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You had the star.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You have to keep your star on, with Juden-- Jew-- written on it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sometimes, in the wintertime, people, ordinary people, they see you, and first they looked around left and right, and nobody sees them, they might have given you an apple or give you something to eat.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you know, they were sympathetic to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, where-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was nothing else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nobody else left in Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we, as the young people, were the only ones.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now, there's a story I didn't tell before, but I would like to really put it in.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My father and mother were still in Cologne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, they followed me to Cologne.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, you know, I seen them once in every two weeks from the kibbutz [HEBREW] and went to them and, you know, and had maybe dinner and things like that.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in Paderborn, in 1942, all of a sudden, the head of the-- the organization there, the kibbutz-- what was his name, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Stein?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or what-- it doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was called to the telephone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Manfred, your father is on the telephone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes, come in here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we went in the office.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he and my father called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He said, Manfred, we will be evacuated within the next four or five days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Do you want to come with us?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We want you should come with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said, Papa, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[SPEAKING GERMAN] I don't want to come.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I knew already what it all was, naturally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother then got to the phone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then she said, [SPEAKING GERMAN]-- he's crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
